    <span class="inline-flex align-items-center h-20 mr-12 px-6 bg-white uppercase font-2xs bold tracking-looser radius-sm">New</span> <p>Stable version of Uniform CSS now officially released! <br class="sm.hidden"><a class="sm.ml-10 bold">Release note</a></p>
